data.description: Spectacular Single-Level, Solar-Powered Home Overlooking the Ocean in Kaunakakai, Molokai.   Welcome to your dream home! This custom-built, one-level house not only offers stunning ocean views but is also packed with premium features for a comfortable island lifestyle. The home includes a two-car garage, complete with additional workshop space and storage.    Step inside to a spacious, open floor plan featuring a large kitchen. With an abundance of storage cabinets, shelves, and a sizeable island, this kitchen is a chef's dream. The property boasts three bedrooms and two baths, all on a single level with no steps, making it accessible and convenient for everyone.   What sets this home apart is its eco-friendly features. Equipped with solar hot water and leased solar electric, it's designed to be energy efficient. Plus, the home features operable skylights that not only allow natural light and airflow but also include rain sensors for those unexpected showers. But the highlight of this home is undoubtedly the large covered patio. Here, you can enjoy the native Hawaiian landscape and the endless ocean vista.   Located close to Kaunakakai, you'll be within easy reach of shopping, dining, and medical facilities. Experience the perfect blend of sustainable living, modern comforts, and natural beauty in this unique home. Your paradise awaits!   The subject property is a "CPR".
